# victor-201.github.io — Environment Variables
# Standard: devops.skill.md Section 3.8
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in real values.
# NEVER commit .env with real values — it is gitignored.
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Spline 3D scene public URL (safe to expose — it's a viewer URL, not a secret key)
# Get it from: https://spline.design → your scene → Export → Viewer URL
VITE_SPLINE_SCENE_URL=https://prod.spline.design/your-scene-id/scene.splinecode

# (Optional) Analytics / tracking — fill in if you add a service later
# VITE_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX
